trans-unit.source: Represents a date selection range in a month calendar control.
trans-unit.target: Monthcalendar 컨트롤에서 날짜 선택 범위를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRange is the date or dates selected and highlighted on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> control.
trans-unit.target: SelectionRange는 날짜 또는 날짜를 선택한 상태에서 강조 표시는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>컨트롤.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>

trans-unit.source: If only one date is selected, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> property values will be equal.
trans-unit.target: 한 날짜를 선택 하는 경우에는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A>속성 값이 같습니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRange can be changed by the user clicking a date while dragging the mouse pointer across the desired dates, or you can set the range in code.
trans-unit.target: 코드의 범위를 설정할 수 있습니다 또는 SelectionRange 원하는 날짜에서 마우스 포인터를 끄는 동안 날짜를 클릭 하 여 변경할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, you might want to have the user enter a date range into two <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox> controls or two <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker> controls and set the SelectionRange based on those dates.
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어 사용자가 두 개로 날짜 범위를 입력 하 게 하려면 수 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>컨트롤 또는 두 개의 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker>컨트롤과 SelectionRange 해당 날짜에 따라 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DateTimePicker> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> values are set to `null` when this constructor is used.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A>값으로 설정 되며 `null` 이 생성자를 사용 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"></xref> class with the specified selection range.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref> 지정 된 선택 범위를 사용 하 여 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> property values are assigned the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> property values of the assigned <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A>속성 값이 할당 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A>속성 값이 할당된 된 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>개체입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.End%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange.Start%2A>

trans-unit.source: The existing <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 기존 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref> 된 지정 된 시작 및 종료 날짜입니다.

trans-unit.target: 종료 날짜 및 시간 선택 범위의 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.target: 시작 날짜 및 시간 선택 범위의 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.target: 시작 <xref:System.DateTime>범위의 값입니다.</xref:System.DateTime>
